Use new_york_subway and select subway_ridership_2013_present dataset from bigquery public dataset
calculation to understand riders in every year

query 1:

SELECT  station_name,ridership_2013,ridership_2014,
ridership_2014-ridership_2013 as ridership_2014_raw FROM `bigquery-public-data.new_york_subway.subway_ridership_2013_present`  


query 2: calculating average

SELECT  station_name,ridership_2013,ridership_2014,
(ridership_2014+ridership_2013+ridership_2015+ridership_2016)/4 as average FROM `bigquery-public-data.new_york_subway.subway_ridership_2013_present` 

